Koornwinder, Tom H.(NL-AMSTM) 
Fast wavelet transforms and Calderón-Zygmund operators. (English. English summary) 
Wavelets: an elementary treatment of theory and applications, 161--182, 
Ser. Approx. Decompos., 1, 
World Sci. Publishing, River Edge, NJ, 1993. 

